data.title: Alumnus Bob Moritz: "New World, New Skills"
data.meta_description: SUNY Oswego alumnus Robert E. Moritz ’85, the global chairman of PwC, will be back on the campus of his alma mater to talk about the future of the workplace and the global trends he sees working with clients and stakeholders around the world. Registration details to come when available., powered by Localist, the Community Event Platform
data.text: SUNY Oswego alumnus Robert E. Moritz ’85, the global chairman of PwC, will be back on the campus of his alma mater to talk about the future of the workplace and the global trends he sees working with clients and stakeholders around the world. Registration details to come when available.
